{"tid":660832,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"依加啲中小學連學中文都用大陸語法","createTime":"2018-05-11T04:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T04:58:19.000Z","uid":108813,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e418613b7b185b172b07e4541b5f4f8f91f48bd","tid":660832,"uid":108813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/123546_8a3230d42d28df265afec92769d2da67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F123546_8a3230d42d28df265afec92769d2da67.png&h=6cf981cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖源fb <br />\n<br />\n「得去買了」根本就係大陸啲口語term嚟<br />\n香港人不嬲書面語講開「要去買了」<br />\n「小玩藝兒」又係，個兒根本又係大陸兒化音<br />\n香港人書面語都係講「小玩兒」<br />\n<br />\n啲00後9成講普通話又學埋哂啲大陸term，應該都唔差在寫埋簡體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心痛，作為90後，見住廣東話由主流到依加係香港開始消逝緊"},{"pid":"efd920272c2fd6a06fe3fa6333edaf2171f72cfc","tid":660832,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"普教中"},{"pid":"ed5348645b47d55bebd86780f7bc6e2e46ee6365","tid":660832,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:48:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"baf8ac58d99d4360453524195c1b4fc66392e170","tid":660832,"uid":39701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:51:11.000Z","msg":"小玩意 喎 咩小玩兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02126bd998bb184bd12969c4eaf08a24ccfb9e1","tid":660832,"uid":9286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed5348645b47d55bebd86780f7bc6e2e46ee6365","tid":660832,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:48:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"香港高官同賤種蝗一樣咁賤"},{"pid":"c86c463f72fb8de81813772712fd15ab6d7d3545","tid":660832,"uid":39701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime